[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    108[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - The architecture does not expose any public endpoints; all data flow is internal (S3, DynamoDB, Step Functions, Lambda are all VPC-internal or use VPC endpoints).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    109[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - No egress to the public internet is required for the pipeline as described (all AWS service calls can be routed through VPC endpoints).
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    110[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
