[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    116[0m:[38;5;10m[49m - **Problem:** The VPC endpoint list names S3, CloudWatch Logs, and KMS but omits the SageMaker API endpoint (`com.amazonaws.{region}.sagemaker.api`) and the SageMaker Runtime endpoint (`com.amazonaws.{region}.sagemaker.runtime`), which are required for the training job to communicate with the SageMaker control plane when running inside a VPC. Also omits the DynamoDB gateway endpoint, which the Lambda loader needs if it runs in the VPC. Additionally, does not distinguish gateway endpoints (S3, DynamoDB) from interface endpoints (CloudWatch Logs, KMS, SageMaker API, SageMaker Runtime).
